data.description: Are you looking for the perfect 2-story open concept home, with the NEWEST features, SMART home technology, & stunning interior designs? Look no further than the 2023 Hawthorn at our Madison Hill community in Spokane Valley. Easy access from the garage leads you right to the open concept kitchen & living room. The 2-tone paint & bright trim, alluring color changing fireplace, designer-inspired “Simply White” quartz countertops, kitchen backsplash featuring a stunning fusion of cloud grey & polished artic white tiles, 36” staggered cabinets with soft close drawers & chrome fixtures, scratch & fade resistant Mohawk Revwood flooring in charming Rustic Rye Chestnut, all work together to create the perfect canvas for designing your life.  2nd level includes a spacious primary suite w/ a roomy walk-in shower, double sinks & a walk-in closet. Laundry room is aptly located next to the primary bedroom.  This  2023  SMART house boasts copious amounts of storage, plenty of room for all of your projects, and more!
